*.egg-info/
.DS_Store
# Transient scratch files passing data from `prepare` to `publish` within
# a single workflow run. Committing these was a bug: yesterday's committed
# copy conflicts with today's on `git pull --rebase`, and git writes
# conflict markers straight into the JSON, corrupting it for the publish
# step. They have no value in git history (output/topics/ is the
# intentional, committed transparency artifact).
output/package-*.json
